--skip-deploy`. The test rewrite checklist item is functionally complete. I was in the process of checking off the spec item and updating the history file when this summary was requested. The TodoWrite shows task 4 \"Check off spec item and update history\" as `in_progress`.\n\n9. Optional Next Step:\n   Complete the current checklist item by:\n   1. Edit spec.md to check off the test item: change `- [ ] [test] Rewrite solana/tests/coinflip.ts...` to `- [x] [test] Rewrite solana/tests/coinflip.ts... (done: iteration 14)`\n   2. Append iteration 14 summary to history.md documenting: test rewrite (26 tests), cancel_match bug fix, Anchor.toml test runner change, tsx dependency addition\n   3. Output a plain summary since more checklist items remain (2 more unchecked items)\n\n   Per the autonomous loop rules: \"If the targeted check PASSES: Check the item off in the spec... Append a brief summary to the history file.\"\n\nIf you need specific details from before compaction (like exact code snippets, error messages, or content you generated), read the full transcript at: /home/vscode/.claude/projects/-workspaces-rng-utopia/26c7f4cc-b2b2-41aa-85e9-beee2a3d95f1.jsonl\nPlease continue the conversation from where we left off without asking the user any further questions. Continue with the last task that you were asked to work on."}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"26c7f4cc-b2b2-41aa-85e9-beee2a3d95f1","uuid":"8501f77c-3c03-45fc-8b60-3f7b3af194d2","isSynthetic":true}
