 73→- **Log**: iteration-004.log\n    74→\n    75→## Iteration 5 — pause.rs\n    76→\n    77→Created `solana/shared/src/pause.rs` with:\n    78→- `PauseError::PlatformPaused` and `PauseError::GamePaused` error codes\n    79→- `check_not_paused(global_paused: bool, game_paused: bool) -> Result<()>` — global pause takes precedence\n    80→- 4 unit tests: both unpaused → Ok, global paused → PlatformPaused, game paused → GamePaused, both paused → PlatformPaused (precedence)\n    81→\n    82→Updated `lib.rs` to re-export `pause` module.\n    83→\n    84→**Verification**: `cargo test -p rng-shared` — 22 tests passed (18 existing + 4 new).\n    85→\n    86→## Iteration 5 — 2026-02-25T21:49:13Z — OK\n    87→- **Log**: iteration-005.log\n    88→\n    89→## Iteration 6 — escrow.rs\n    90→\n    91→Created `solana/shared/src/escrow.rs` with:\n    92→- `EscrowError::InsufficientEscrowBalance` error code\n    93→- `transfer_lamports_from_pda(pda, recipient, amount) -> Result<()>` — direct lamport manipulation via `try_borrow_mut_lamports` with balance check\n    94→- `transfer_lamports_to_pda(from, pda, amount, system_program_info) -> Result<()>` — system program CPI transfer with explicit lifetime parameter `'a` on all `AccountInfo<'a>` refs\n    95→- Doc-test examples (marked `ignore` — need runtime context, deferred to bankrun in Phase C)\n    96→\n    97→Updated `lib.rs` to re-export `escrow` module.\n    98→\n    99→**Verification**: `anchor build` succeeded (release + test profiles). `cargo test -p rng-shared` — 22 unit tests passed, 2 doc-tests correctly ignored.\n   100→\n   101→## Iteration 6 — 2026-02-25T21:53:37Z — OK\n   102→- **Log**: iteration-006.log\n   103→\n   104→## Iteration 7 — cpi.rs\n   105→\n   106→Created `solana/shared/src/cpi.rs` with:\n   107→- `update_player_profile_cpi(platform_program, profile, authority, signer_seeds, total_games_delta, wins_delta, total_wagered_delta, total_won_delta) -> Result<()>` — CPI helper for platform program's `update_pla